name: Trap Reactor - NG
text: You can Special Summon this card (from your hand or GY) by sending 1 "Reactor" card you control to the GY except "Trap Reactor - NG". If this card is Summoned by its own effect: You can add 1 "System Overload" from your Deck to your hand. Once per turn, if your opponent activates a Trap Card or effect: You can negate that effect, and if you do, set that card to your Spell & Trap zone. If you activate a Trap Card owned by your opponent: Inflict 1000 damage to your opponent.
